&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The following table will enable us to know how tense changes into &lt;strong&gt;Indirect speech:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

